Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐 这位是皆野总编
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么跟爱徒交往的是哪一位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有和他交往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然被狠狠的吐糟了 明明我是总编来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:55.83,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&HF3727B&\3c&HFFFFFF&}主编的审查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在爱徒那里做助手多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 一年左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟爱徒进展到哪步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他揉过你胸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个问题和现在有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你被揉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果事故也算的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚…刚见面的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子真能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么也让我揉一揉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱徒就能揉 我就不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总编…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然对爱徒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她这么小 好歹也是总编
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她想这么做应该有她的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以把胸罩拿掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这触感相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一本满足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在说漫画的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…这跟揉胸到底有什么关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想揉一下而已 不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你刚才说有关系的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得如果我在意你的胸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法对漫画作出正确的评价
Comment: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总编 到开会的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 已经到时间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 关于漫画的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.09,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H87C814&\3c&HFFFFFF&}再加把劲吧 总结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想像的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我开始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被无视了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:45.33,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H856DF6&\3c&HFFFFFF&}了解女生的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等足须小姐 有时无视比报警更残酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个我以为你觉醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐 你把我当变态了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有需要怀疑的余地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新的兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为见张跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「要想把漫画变的更好 就学下女生的心思」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就想从外表做起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你做什么都好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最起码也应该把腿毛刮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 把假发也带上 做戏做全套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做全套…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 感觉挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得这么正式 反而不会觉得不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来说不定就能了解女生的心思了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么谈吐也要像个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行 为 举 止 也 要 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我今天就用这身打扮来工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 我画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 我把茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑奈小姐的头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光滑如丝 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 感觉看到的世界都不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去的话 我就辞职吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我女生的魅力还跟大家相差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师一定能理解女生真正的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲…玲奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我接下来要做的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 变得更累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡相真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我要奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你想做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是理解母性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女生究极的心思的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来…慢用吧 濑奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是为人母的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好咸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.72,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H09E778&\3c&HFFFFFF&}去死!! 去死!! 濑奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死 去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没画好？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为攻略新出的GalGame太耗时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是这也是为了画漫画而学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这所谓的「学习」用了多长时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天十小时…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.95,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H09E778&\3c&HFFFFFF&}玩太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天内给我完成八成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也不准玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见张小姐真有耐心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的话 要是每次都这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会要求换其他人负责老师你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要换的话…会换个怎么样的人来？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会换个老师决定不会反抗的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如钢筋肌肉男？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:18.52,Comment,,0,0,0,,想把你抱在怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢筋…肌肉男！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 全部画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个 好像是下回的分镜稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 完成的质量也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见张就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要钢筋肌肉男！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一话的原稿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经画好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还画好两话分镜稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\bord2\c&H020404&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(447,354)}又过了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两话画好的原稿跟之后的五话分镜稿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 我们是月刊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\bord2\c&H020404&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(413,356)}又再过了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只画好四话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要换钢筋肌肉男给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最近到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 其实…
